      <title>以色列持续袭击迫使伊朗作出不情愿的回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/iran-pushed-into-reluctant-response-by-sustained-israel-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几个月来，伊朗将军和神职人员一再表现出不愿发动战争的态度，但以色列对伊朗地区实力造成的破坏程度让他们别无选择，只能进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/iran-pushed-into-reluctant-response-by-sustained-israel-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法院批准对美国大选的投注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/betting-on-us-elections-get-fresh-greenlight-from-appeals-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国 11 月大选投票前五周，美国上诉法院为大量投注奠定了基础，如今美国人可以再次合法地对国会选举进行下注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/betting-on-us-elections-get-fresh-greenlight-from-appeals-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将部署 1000 名士兵援助北卡罗来纳州海伦飓风</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-to-deploy-1-000-troops-to-aid-north-carolina-after-helene</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他指示五角大楼派遣多达 1,000 名现役军人，协助北卡罗来纳州的恢复工作，之后他们将前往受飓风海伦袭击最严重的州之一，亲自视察飓风造成的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/biden-to-deploy-1-000-troops-to-aid-north-carolina-after-helene</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 1000 亿美元艾滋病项目致力于非洲制造业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/us-s-100-billion-hiv-program-commits-to-african-manufacturing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员表示，美国总统艾滋病紧急救援计划承诺在非洲大陆进行检测和疫苗研发，该计划是全球为抗击单一疾病提供的最大资金承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/us-s-100-billion-hiv-program-commits-to-african-manufacturing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称，借助援助和疫苗，可以遏制痘病毒传播</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/mpox-spread-can-be-nipped-in-the-bud-with-aid-vaccines-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国计划向中部非洲地区提供 5 亿美元援助和疫苗，以遏制迅速蔓延的 mpox 亚变种疫情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/mpox-spread-can-be-nipped-in-the-bud-with-aid-vaccines-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:01:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱希望阿根廷人为他实现经济美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/milei-wants-argentines-to-dollarize-the-economy-for-him-shock-therapy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱伊似乎已经放弃了阿根廷经济突然正式美元化的愿景。这位政治家在去年的总统竞选期间曾建议炸毁央行的比索印钞机，但现在他不再谈论这件事了。相反，他希望他的同胞为他完成这项工作。一美元一美元，一比索一比索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/milei-wants-argentines-to-dollarize-the-economy-for-him-shock-therapy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙称过度监管将使欧洲落后于美国和中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/macron-warns-that-eu-needs-radical-change-is-lagging-china-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙对欧盟前景表示悲观，他警告称，缺乏投资和过多的监管将使欧盟缺乏竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/macron-warns-that-eu-needs-radical-change-is-lagging-china-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:59:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
